                    <h2>About This Project</h2>
                    <p>This project was made in the context of a video editing class with the objective of stylized documentary. The objective was learning proper editing techniques while maintaining a distinct visual identity.</b></p>
                    <p>The documentary tries to simulate a body cam of a special agent investigating a village where a virus (inspired by Resident Evil / Biohazard) has amde animals to be aggressive towards humans. Using this concept, I created a short story and started shooting as many scenes as I could, walking around a village and recording the animals living in its streets. A VHS camera effect was used, and in certain parts of the video text was introduced to simulate the effect used in confidential documents to explain certain aspects of the story.</p>
                    
